{% set species = sinonatrixAnnularisRespImgs %}
{% set translation_link = species[0].nameLowerCaseHyphenated %}

{% extends "_layout_zh.njk" %} 
{% block hrefLanguage %}
         <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en-US" href="https://snakesoftaiwan.com/{{- species[0].nameLowerCaseHyphenated -}}.html" />
         <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://snakesoftaiwan.com/{{- species[0].nameLowerCaseHyphenated -}}.html" />
     <link rel="alternate" hreflang="zh-TW" href="https://snakesoftaiwan.com/{{- species[0].nameLowerCaseHyphenated -}}_zh.html" />
     <link rel="alternate" hreflang="zh" href="https://snakesoftaiwan.com/{{- species[0].nameLowerCaseHyphenated -}}_zh.html" />
{% endblock %}
{% block metaDescription %}
    "{{ species[0].chineseName }} {{ species[0].chineseNameRomanized }}. {{ species[0].danger }}, 最大體長: 100 cm, 稀少蛇類。最長在北部海拔500m以上被人發現。赤腹游蛇為夜行性蛇類，通常出沒在水田、沼澤和池塘等等溼地區域。牠以青蛙、蝌蚪還有魚類為食。"
{% endblock %}
{% block headLinks %}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/swiperJsGallery.min.css">       
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/infoPages.min.css">
{% endblock %}
{% block csp %}
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy" content="default-src 'none'; img-src 'self' https://www.google-analytics.com www.google-analytics.com https://stats.g.doubleclick.net; script-src 'self' https://www.google-analytics.com https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/dompurify/2.2.6/purify.min.js https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js; media-src 'self'; connect-src 'self' https://www.google-analytics.com www.google-analytics.com https://stats.g.doubleclick.net; style-src 'self' https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css; font-src 'self' data: application/font-woff">
{% endblock %}
{% block title %}
    {{ species[0].name }} - {{ species[0].chineseName }}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    
    <div class="header-box">
        <h1 class="header--species" lang="en-US">{{ species[0].name }}</h1>
        <h2 class="header--name" lang="en-US">{{ species[0].commonName }}</h2>
        <h2 class="header--name">{{ species[0].chineseName }}</h2>
        <h3 class="header--status">{{ species[0].statusChinese }}</h3>
        <h4 class="header--danger">{{ species[0].dangerChinese }}</h4>
    </div>                      

    {% include "partials/_swiper-responsive-images-modal_zh.njk" %}
    {% include "partials/_swiper-responsive-images-nonModal_zh.njk" %}
    {% include "partials/_swiper-responsive-images-thumbs_zh.njk" %}
    
    <div class="text-box-container text-box-container-info">
        <div class="text-box--species">
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    家族
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    黃頷蛇科，<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natricinae" lang="en-US">Natricinae</a> 亞種
                    <br>
                    <span lang="en-US">Colubridae, subfamily <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natricinae">Natricinae</a></span> 
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    最大體長
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text" lang="en-US">
                    100 cm
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    台灣棲地分布
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    稀少蛇類。最長在北部海拔500m以上被人發現。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    世界棲地分布
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    台灣，南中國（福建，江西，浙江，安徽，江蘇，廣東，廣西，海南，湖南，湖北，四川）。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    外觀描述
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text" lang="en-US">
                    This snake is small to medium in size; total length up to 106 cm. There are 17-19 (19 at mid-body) rows of scales, which are keeled except those on the flanks. Head is oval; body is stout and round; tail is moderately long. Eye is medium-sized; iris is dark brown to black, slightly dappled with irregular areas of yellow brown, and pupil is black, round, surrounded by light yellow brown ring, sometimes off center, i.e. toward upper part of eye. Tongue is fresh color to red, darkened by diffuse black pigment, fork tips lighter than stem. Upper head is uniform dark gray to gray brown. The labials are yellow to yellow tan, with vertical or oblique black bands at sutures. Upper body and tail are gray to olive brown, with irregularly shaped black designs on sides. The lateral designs may have diffuse white to cream centers, with scattered spots of white or cream nearby, and usually continuous with ventral bands. Ventral head is dirty white to cream; the posterior gulars may possess black margins. Ventral neck is dirty white, tinted with orange which progressively more intense posteriorly; ventral body and tail also bear scattered quadrangular marks of prominent black pigment which are irregularly arranged on sides. Anal scale is divided and subcaudals are paired.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    生態描述
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text"> 	
                    赤腹游蛇為夜行性蛇類，通常出沒在水田、沼澤和池塘等等溼地區域。牠以青蛙、蝌蚪還有魚類為食。胎生，春夏季交配，母蛇於夏末到秋季間產下一窩 1 -14 條的幼蛇。初生幼蛇約 20cm長。 
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    學名與俗名
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <div class="info-box-paragraph">
                        <span lang="en-US"><i>Sinonatrix</i></span>: "<span lang="en-US"><i>Sino</i></span>" 是新拉丁文 "中華、中國"; <span lang="en-US"><i>natrix</i></span> 是拉丁文 "水蛇、游蛇";
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-box-paragraph">
                        <span lang="en-US"><i>annularis</i></span> 是來自拉丁文，有 "環狀、帶狀" 之意。
                    </div>
                    赤腹游蛇 、半紋蛇、赤鏈華游蛇、紅豬母、水赤鏈游蛇。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    相關連結
                </div>
                <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species" lang="en-US">
                    <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://reptile-database.reptarium.cz/species.php?genus=Sinonatrix&species=annularis">Reptile Database</a></li>
                    <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://ub-dok.uni-trier.de/diss/diss45/20030217/20030217.pdf"><span lang="zh-TW">台灣華游蛇屬的族群生態</span> - Population Ecology of Genus <i>Sinonatrix</i> in Taiwan</a> (PDF)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="translator-name">翻譯:周信甫</div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Swiper JS -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Initialize Swiper -->
    <script   src="js/mySwiper.min.js"></script>

{% endblock %}